data.description: Maintenance Free, Lakefront Living.  3 bed, 2.5 bath, custom home, comes with an extra lot and 2 boat slips. Main floor primary suite. Main level open concept Kitchen, dining area and living area open to deck all with great view of Baldwin Lake. Lower level has 2 beds, 1 bath,  large living areas and plenty of storage.  Community includes Beach area, Pavilion, Fire Pit, Volleyball court and 3 acres of open space. Baldwin Lake is a 265 acre, spring fed, all sports lake, located 2 hours from Chicago and 25 mins to Notre Dame.  Association maintains, all landscaping, snow removal, trash, and pier install.
